1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if I told you your heart has secret gates?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,800
Heart valves control blood flow, ensuring it moves in the right direction.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,200
But how do they do this?

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,200
There are four main valves: tricuspid, pulmonary, mitral, and aortic.

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:17,200
Each plays a critical role.

6
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:20,800
They open and close with each heartbeat, preventing backflow.

7
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,200
But what happens when they malfunction?

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,400
Valve diseases can lead to serious health issues.

9
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,800
Monitoring your heart health is essential!

10
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:32,000
Curious about how to keep your heart healthy?

11
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,600
Follow for more insights!
